{"tid":1877840,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"你班的士佬手停口停又好 無哂生意又好都係自己同行攞黎賤","createTime":"2020-02-13T08:54:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T01:48:15.000Z","uid":171273,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"55d7da6978af70d78ea39ab0fbd5a09baf780982","tid":1877840,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"利申 係港島某外資銀行做BO<br />\n<br />\n1月頭開始驚搭車咁多人中招 已經朝朝搭的士<br />\n<br />\n早幾日見到深圳灣封關果晚條的士龍之後無再搭過的士 轉左搭uber<br />\n<br />\n身邊識好多人都係咁 而家經過平時要排隊上車d的士站都無哂人返工爭的士<br />\n<br />\n如果各位的士佬之後無哂生意要怪就怪班有份爭住做支耶人生意既賤種的士狗倒米<br />\n<br />\n排兩個鐘入深圳灣接一程客搞撚到幾個月無哂生意<br />\n<br />\n弱撚智到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6788158ca8b9ff868cf85b08e752c45c56f9c6","tid":1877840,"uid":320135,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"就係可憐啲黃嘅DC叔叔囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2278ac456c752e7974a6ef8f2020e2a9d24c70dc","tid":1877840,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:29:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775a96460d7a9c68682617d76a683879b31c429c","tid":1877840,"uid":45523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:31:03.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n我之前都係日日搭的士返工<br />\n而家轉咗搭uber"},{"pid":"9cdd3c3c39155d1cf777af639358d75db62e9881","tid":1877840,"uid":2154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:31:13.000Z","msg":"手足黎"},{"pid":"fd53a10173d40958a38c43e1bf2f39bdd8a72a27","tid":1877840,"uid":208940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"小弟每當提起話的士司機撞向市民事件，的士狗都話做得啱，令人氣結"},{"pid":"ddeb67415204acc1d252b79b5c5fe7aed10b0892","tid":1877840,"uid":139082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"而家call的一定call黃的tg"},{"pid":"5af421839943d08e72ddb8b4085c3fdbcecb4a0b